      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but it feels like there's a contradiction there. if we give exemptions to religious groups, aren't we basically saying their values are more important than the laws that apply to everyone else? it seems like letting them opt out actually makes the state less neutral because it gives them special treatment. wouldn't that eventually just weaken the whole idea of a secular government?",
